---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Monti Studio">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-32">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight max-w-3xl">
      A small studio with
      <span class="text-neutral-500">big ambitions.</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p>Monti Studio is a creative agency based in London. We work with brands and businesses to design and build digital products that stand out.</p>
        <p>We believe in simplicity, craft, and delivering work that actually makes a difference. No fluff, no bloat — just thoughtful design and solid engineering.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p>Whether it's a brand identity, a marketing site, or a full web application, we bring the same level of care and attention to every project.</p>
        <p>We're selective about who we work with because we want to do our best work for every client.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-neutral-800/50 py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Want to work together?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-4 text-lg">We'd love to hear about your project.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block mt-8 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-neutral-950 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
